\c 5
\s UMozisi loAroni baphambi kukaFaro
\p
\v 1 Emva kwalokho-ke uMozisi loAroni bahamba bathi kuFaro: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli: Bayekele abantu bami bahambe, bangigcinele umkhosi enkangala\x + 10.9; 12.9,14.\x*.
\v 2 Kodwa uFaro wathi: Ingubani iN\nd kosi\x + 2 Kho. 18.35. Jobe 21.15.\x*\nd* ukuthi ngilalele ilizwi layo, ngiyekele uIsrayeli ahambe? Kangiyazi iN\nd kosi\nd*, futhi kangiyikumyekela uIsrayeli ahambe.
\v 3 Basebesithi: UNkulunkulu wamaHebheru\x + 3.18; 7.16.\x* uhlangane lathi; ake usiyekele sihambe uhambo lwensuku ezintathu enkangala, siyihlabele iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu, hlezi isehlele\x + Hlu. 15.12. 1 Kho. 2.25,32.\x* ngomatshayabhuqe wesifo kumbe ngenkemba.
\v 4 Kodwa inkosi yeGibhithe yathi kubo: Kungani, Mozisi loAroni, lisusa abantu emisebenzini yabo? Yanini emithwalweni yenu!
\v 5 UFaro wasesithi: Khangelani, abantu belizwe sebebanengi, kanti liyabaphumuza emithwalweni yabo\x + 1.11.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Ngalolosuku uFaro waselaya abaqhubi besibhalo\x + 5.10,13,14; 1.11; 3.7.\x* besizwe lezinduna\x + 5.14,15,19.\x* zaso, esithi:
\v 7 Lingabe lisabanika abantu amahlanga okwenza izitina njengamandulo\x + 4.10; 5.8,14. Gen. 31.2. 1 Sam. 19.7.\x*; kabahambe bona bayezibuthela amahlanga;
\v 8 lenani lezitina abalenze mandulo lizabamisela lona, lingaphunguli kulo; ngoba bayavilapha; yikho bekhala besithi: Siyekeleni siyehlabela uNkulunkulu wethu.
\v 9 Yenzani umsebenzi ube nzima kakhulu phezu kwamadoda, ukuze basebenze kuwo, bangalaleli amazwi enkohliso.
\p
\v 10 Abaqhubi besibhalo babantu baphuma, lezinduna zabo, bakhuluma ebantwini besithi: Utsho njalo uFaro: Kangiyikulinika amahlanga;
\v 11 hambani lina, lizithathele amahlanga lapho elingawathola khona; kodwa umsebenzi wenu kakuyikuphungulwa lutho kuwo.
\v 12 Abantu basebehlakazeka elizweni lonke leGibhithe ukuze babuthe izidindi zibe ngamahlanga.
\v 13 Abaqhubi besibhalo ba\add ba\add*haluzelisa besithi: Qedani imisebenzi yenu, umlandu wosuku ngosuku lwawo, njengamhla kulamahlanga.
\v 14 Njalo izinduna zabantwana bakoIsrayeli, abaqhubi besibhalo bakaFaro abababekela zona, zatshaywa, kuthiwa: Kaliqedanga ngani umsebenzi wenu omisiweyo wokwenza izitina njengamandulo, layizolo lalamuhla?
\p
\v 15 Izinduna zabantwana bakoIsrayeli zasezisiza, zakhala kuFaro zathi: Wenzelani kanje ezincekwini zakho?
\v 16 Amahlanga kawanikwa inceku zakho, kanti bathi kithi: Yenzani izitina. Khangela-ke, inceku zakho ziyatshaywa; kodwa icala ngelabantu bakho.
\v 17 Kodwa wathi: Lina lingamavila, lingamavila; ngalokhu lithi: Siyekeleni siyehlabela iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 18 Khathesi-ke hambani, lisebenze; kodwa amahlanga kaliyikuwanikwa, kanti lizaletha inani lezitina.
\v 19 Izinduna zabantwana bakoIsrayeli zasezibona ukuthi zazisebubini, nxa kuthiwa: Kaliyikuphungula ezitineni zenu, umlandu wosuku ngosuku lwawo.
\p
\v 20 Zasezihlangana loMozisi loAroni ababemi ukubahlangabeza ekuphumeni kwabo kuFaro;
\v 21 zasezisithi kubo: IN\nd kosi\nd* ilibone yahlulele; ngoba lenze iphunga lethu libe livumba emehlweni kaFaro lemehlweni enceku zakhe; linike inkemba esandleni sabo ukuze basibulale\x + 6.9.\x*.
\v 22 UMozisi wasebuyela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni wathi: Nkosi, wenzeleni okubi kulesisizwe? Kungani ungithumile?
\v 23 Ngoba selokhu ngaya kuFaro ukukhuluma ebizweni lakho, wenzile okubi kulesisizwe; futhi kawusikhululanga lokusikhulula isizwe sakho.
